00:34:02.686 --> 00:34:04.310
So I want to say two
things about that.

00:34:04.310 --> 00:34:06.490
I think the first
thing to recognize

00:34:06.490 --> 00:34:10.139
is that it's not just our
knowledge of the influence

00:34:10.139 --> 00:34:14.900
and persuasion process that
extends and grows over time.

00:34:14.900 --> 00:34:19.600
Our knowledge of all information
extends and grows as well.

00:34:19.600 --> 00:34:25.540
So it's not that we are
growing in our insights

00:34:25.540 --> 00:34:27.940
about one particular field
to the expense of others.

00:34:27.940 --> 00:34:30.630
So we are constantly
being overloaded.

00:34:30.630 --> 00:34:34.670
So our need to have quick and
efficient mechanisms for making

00:34:34.670 --> 00:34:37.156
decisions won't
wane, if anything,

00:34:37.156 --> 00:34:38.239
it will actually increase.

00:34:39.304 --> 00:34:40.679
But I think there
is a case to be

00:34:40.679 --> 00:34:43.860
made when it comes to
the particular tactic

00:34:43.860 --> 00:34:46.098
or individual strategy
that someone uses.

00:34:46.098 --> 00:34:47.139
I'll give you an example.

00:34:48.489 --> 00:34:50.420
So it turns out
that if you've ever

00:34:50.420 --> 00:34:53.600
